Name: project_priority_weight
Description: Weight assigned to project priority in planning

Name: team_capacity_utilization
Description: Percentage of team capacity used in sprint planning

Name: task_assignment_binary
Description: Binary decision: assign worker to task

Name: sprint_inclusion_flag
Description: Whether a user story is included in current sprint

Name: feature_release_flag
Description: Whether a feature is included in next release

Name: worker_availability_hours
Description: Number of hours a worker is available per week

Name: story_point_estimate
Description: Estimated story points for a user story

Name: effort_allocation_per_task
Description: Planned effort in hours for a task

Name: blocker_resolution_time
Description: Estimated time in days to resolve a blocker

Name: documentation_completeness
Description: Score indicating completeness of feature documentation

Name: release_planned_date_deviation
Description: Deviation in days from planned release date

Name: retrospective_improvement_count
Description: Number of improvement actions from retrospective

Name: scrum_board_column_index
Description: Index of current column for a task on scrum board
